The U.S.-Japan Agreement is a good deal for the American people and our economy. This agreement will open the Japanese market for southern Minnesota exports, especially pork and beef. We need to support the Japan agreement and pass USMCA.  -JH

Today, I introduced the “American Workforce Empowerment Act” with @CongressmanJVD. Our legislation will empower the American workers by enabling the use of pre-tax 529 savings accounts to pursue vocational training and apprenticeships for skilled labor professions.  -JH #MN01
